OL,6,FGet the tone wrong and there could be
OL,7,Freal trouble.
OL,9,FMy own sense is that the ratings on
OL,10,FSaturday will serve as a reminder of
OL,11,Fwhat most of the BBC's supporters
OL,12,Frightly expect of it.
OL,14,FMany who may not consider themselves
OL,15,Froyalists will no doubt still want to
OL,16,Fwatch the ceremony and a moment of
OL,17,Fhistory.
OL,19,FIt should be a reminder of the BBC's
OL,20,Fpower to bring diverse audiences
OL,21,Ftogether and our shared collective
OL,22,Fexperience.
OL,3,CBBC: dividing public opinion and
OL,4,Cbringing people together
