OL,6,FIndeed if that is not the single most
OL,7,Fspecial role of a major broadcaster
OL,8,Fin a fragmented society then what is
OL,9,Fthe point of it?
OL,11,FThe BBC can bring us together `
OL,12,Fwhether we are cheering King Charles
OL,13,For simply wish to see the ceremony.
OL,15,FAnd no doubt it will attract far more
OL,16,Fviewers than ITV 1 no matter how good
OL,17,Ftheir coverage is.
